Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}放到最后再说吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.46,0:21:50.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}现实中满是不如意
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.86,0:21:55.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那就都塞到瓶子里
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}准备好参加派对了吗?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不等你了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}另一个故事就要开始了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.07,0:22:07.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数气泡呼呼冒出
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数气泡啵啵破裂
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.75,0:22:13.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}生活就像汽水
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.84,0:22:16.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无论是爸爸妈妈的事
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}还是闷在心底的回忆
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.62,0:22:22.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都会化作气泡消失掉
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}哭泣忧愁又烦恼
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.75,0:22:27.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}无数往事多纷扰
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.04,0:22:31.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}都没关系的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.15,0:22:34.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所有往事尽怀抱
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.65,0:22:36.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}塞进瓶子使劲摇
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.90,0:22:41.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}噗嗤全部释放　大家一起欢笑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}咕噜噜　瞬间满是气泡
